<br>
Also what brought this about this newfound interest in throwing weapons was the discovery by Sasarle of velium throwing weapons in Thurgadin. Including Forin's data, here is the breakdown of throwing weapons. Standard and velium class prices are baseline indifferent via sneaking. Antonican forged items are ommited due to the difficulty in obtaining them.<br>
<br>
<br>
Standard Class<br>
------------------------------<br>
Throwing Knives - Dam 5 Delay 36 (ratio 0.139); range 45; wt 0.5; stack cost 2.5gp<br>
<br>
Shuriken - Dam 4 Delay 26 (ratio .154); Range 60; wt 0.5; stack cost 2.5gp<br>
<br>
Thowing Axe - Dam 6 Delay 30 (ratio 0.200); range 120; wt 1.0; stack cost 7gp<br>
<br>
<br>
Forged Class<br>
------------------------------<br>
Forged Throwing Knives - Dam 5 Delay 35 (ratio 0.143); range 60; wt 0.5; stack cost 2.5pp<br>
<br>
Forged Shuriken - Dam 4 Delay 25 (ratio .160); Range 65; wt 0.5; stack cost 2.5pp<br>
<br>
Forged Thowing Axe - Dam 6 Delay 29 (ratio 0.206); range 125; wt 1.0; stack cost 5pp<br>
<br>
Forged Javelin - Dam 7 Delay 33 (ratio 0.212); range 205; wt 2.0; stack cost 12pp<br>
<br>
<br>
Velium Vendor Class<br>
------------------------------<br>
Velium Throwing Dagger - Dam 6 Delay 36 (ratio 0.167); Range 55; wt 0.3; stack cost 5pp<br>
<br>
Velium Shuriken - Dam 5 Delay 26 (ratio 0.192); Range 70; wt 0.3; stack cost 5pp<br>
<br>
Velium Throwing Spear - Dam 8 Delay 34 (ratio 0.235); Range 210; wt 1.5; single cost 7.8gp (non-stackable)<br>
<br>
Velium Throwing Axe - Dam 7 Delay 30 (ratio 0.233); Range 130; wt 0.8; single cost 5.2gp (non-stackable)<br>
<br>
<br>
Forged Velium Class<br>
------------------------------<br>
Forged Velium Shuriken - Dam 5 Delay 24 (ratio 0.208); Range 75; wt 0.3; cost unknown<br>
<br>
Forged Velium Throwing Knives - data unknown<br>
<br>
Forged Velium Throwing Axe - data unknown<br>
<br>
Forged Velium Javelin - data unknown<br>
<br>
<br>
The best of the following classes...<br>
<br>
Best range - 1) Velium Throwing Spear    2) Forged Javelin<br>
Best damage - 1) Velium Throwing Spear    2) Velium Throwing Axe <br>
Best weight to damage - 1) Forged Velium Shuriken    2) Velium Shuriken<br>
<br>
<br>
To conclude, until more data is found about forged velium weapons, Sasarle will be going with a standard loadout of Velium Shuriken and a speciallized loadout of Forged Javelins. If Velium Throwing Spears were stackable, they would win hands down, but unfortunately, they are not. The only downside to Velium weapons is their exclusive availability in Thurgadin.<br>
<br>
I'll be passing along a ten slot backpack to you Forin to fill with Forged Javelins. You have now been choosen as Sasarle's defense contractor... heh. Just let me know what the bill will be.<br>
<br>
